    • Method Detail

      • startSpectating

        public void startSpectating()
        Switches the player to the PlayerState.SPECTATING state. Launches the player upward with a flight effect. Changes player GameMode to GameMode.ADVENTURE.

      • prepareForGame

        public void prepareForGame()
        Prepares the player for a match. Clears the player's inventory, resets health to the default 20.0, resets food level to 20.0, clears all potion effects, and disables team chat.
